== Recruitment ==

=== Finding the Prince of Cannock ===

The Prince is not at Cannock Castle initially:
1. Travel to Cannock Castle
2. Learn he went to Midenhall
3. Return to Midenhall
4. Learn he went to Spring of Bravery
5. Go to Spring of Bravery
6. Finally meet at Cannock

=== Finding the Princess of Moonbrooke ===

The Princess was cursed into a dog:
1. Find the Mirror of Ra (Swamp Cave)
2. Use it on the dog in Moonbrooke
3. She transforms back and joins

== Party Formation ==

Party order affects combat:
* Position 1 (Hero): Targeted most often
* Position 2 (Cannock): Moderate targeting
* Position 3 (Moonbrooke): Targeted least

Recommended formation:
1. Prince of Midenhall (tank)
2. Prince of Cannock (support)
3. Princess of Moonbrooke (back line)

